snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3741 - Babita Wins a Car?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi 
Special Thanks: Mahesh Vakil, Indu Tarak Mehta
Set Design: Jayant Deshmukh
On-Air Promotion  ( SAB): SAB OAP
Costume Designer: Alka Mehta
Costume Stylist: Ekta Brahmbhatt
Sound Recordist: Shakeel Mansuri 
Cameraman: Aamir Virani
Production Head: Arvind Marchande
Production Controler: Vinod Shishupal
Background Music: Sunil Patni
Online Editors: Vishal Tambe, Sandeep Singh 
Executive Producer: Jatin Yogesh Bajaj
Editor: Dinesh Gosavi, Kaushal Mistry, Devang Modi, Vinod Maurya
Creative Supervision: Krunal Khakhkhar
Operation Head: Sohil Ramani
Written By: Raju Odedra & Rajen Upadhyay
Directors: Harshad Joshi, Malav Suresh Rajda

Television Adaptation and Designed By: Asit Kumarr Modi

Where is Pushpa? Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Hindi Glimpse !!!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3742 - 11 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3742: Khushi Bhet
--------------------------------------------------------
Champaklal is given an explanation of the lucky draw win by Jetha, Bagha, and Nattu Kaka. Jetha is eager to announce the winner, but Nattu Kaka unintentionally reveals Babita Ji's name. Jetha becomes agitated because he wants to reveal Babita Ji's name. Afterward, Jetha promises to repay Bagha and Nattu Kaka financially for their efforts in the program. On the other side, Madhavi and Anjali experience some disappointment about losing the car. Sonu comforts her mother by promising that she will soon own her ideal vehicle. Babita is also eager about taking driving lessons and getting her license. The following event is revealed if you watch the show!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3742, 11 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000216033

snippet.description:

https://youtu.be/XxAB_XVBMZo

மருத்து நீராடி தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை | கனி காணுதல் | தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு
https://youtu.be/0g00MJwEQNw

செல்வம், ஆரோக்கியம், நீண்ட ஆயுள் பெற தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை.   மேலும் கனி காணுதல், அறுசுவை உணவு படைத்தல், வழிபடும் நேரம் என பல தகவல்களை திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

செல்வம், ஆரோக்கியம், நீண்ட ஆயுள் பெற தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டை வரவேற்று வழிபடும் முறை.   மேலும் கனி காணுதல், அறுசுவை உணவு படைத்தல், வழிபடும் நேரம் என பல தகவல்களை திருமதி. தேச மங்கையர்க்கரசி அம்மா அவர்கள் அளித்துள்ளார். 

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

# தமிழ் வருட பிறப்பு 
# Tamil New Year
# தமிழ்ப் புத்தாண்டு

Let's take you men's wear shopping for the festive wedding season at the most happening place in Hyderabad in the Banjara Hills at the Asuka Store

Walk in and experience the medley of heritage and old world charm with the modern, just like their collection, and exult in the ritual of fine dressing, an experience that's gonna leave you savouring in the fragrance of tommorow!

The design house hails from Delhi where they've been manufacturers of men's wear garments for over 35 years. From ceremonial suits for festive occasions, Sherwanis for Weddings, ornate Bandhgalas, Kurtas, indowestern attire in wide range of hues, fabrics, embroidery, and matching shoes and accesories, it's a one stop shop for men who like to dress the best!

snippet.title: Maharashtra Shaheer Official Trailer | Ankush, Sana | Kedar Shinde | Ajay-Atul | 28 April 2023
snippet.description:
Presenting Official Trailer of most awaited Marathi Movie 2023 "महाराष्ट्र शाहीर MAHARASHTRA SHAHEER" starring Ankush Choudhary, Sana Kedar Shinde. Movie Directed by Kedar Shinde & Music by Ajay-Atul. Exclusively only on @EverestMarathi 

'महाराष्ट्र शाहीर'
अभिमानाने, आदराने आणि प्रेमाने सादर करत आहोत,
बहुचर्चित, बहुप्रतिक्षीत महाराष्ट्राचा महासिनेमा 'महाराष्ट्र शाहीर' चा महाट्रेलर.!!
जना-मनातला आवाज अर्थात शाहीर साबळे यांची भव्य जीवनगाथा २८ एप्रिलपासून महाराष्ट्राच्या प्रत्येक  चित्रपटगृहात..

Shahir Krushnarao Sable began his journey as a simple folk singer, and reached great heights when he used his music for so much more. When state of Maharashtra was formed, it was Shahir Sable’s immortal voice that took the anthem ‘Jai Jai Maharashtra Maza’ to every household. This is his story.

http://bit.ly/3lua1cx

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3741 - 10 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3741: Popatlal Wins The Honeymoon Coupon
--------------------------------------------------------
Residents of Gokuldham are impatiently awaiting the announcement of the winner. The announcement of the final two coupon rewards has all of the society's members prepared. Popatlal jumps excitedly as he wins the honeymoon package in his coupon and gets to know that he can avail the prize within a year. The winner is announced by the company as Taarak and Babita get the same starting serial number. Who will take home the car in this jackpot? To find out, watch the episode!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3741, 10 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000215923

snippet.title: अब आलू टिक्की व दही भल्ला इस तरह से बनायें, 1 ही डो से-Instant Aloo Sooji Tikki & Dahi Bhalla Chaat
snippet.description:
No-fry Bhalla Chaat step-by-step, Crispy Aloo ki Tikki, Instant Bhalla Chaat recipe, Instant Bhalla

#bhalla #steetfood #soojikanasta #chaat  

Ingredients for Sooji Aloo Tikki
तेल - Oil - 1 tsp
सूजी - Semolina - 1/2 cup (90 grams)
आलू - Potato - 5 pieces (350 grams)
नमक - Salt - 3/4 tsp
तेल - Oil - 2-3 tsp
जीरा - Cumin Seeds - 1/2 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1 tsp, grated
हींग - Asafoetida - 1/2 pinch
मटर - Pea - 1 cup
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/4 tsp
नमक - Salt - 1/3 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dried mango powder - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander
तेल - Oil - 3-4 tbsp

Ingredients for Dahi Bhalla Chaat Chaat
दही - Curd
मीठी चटनी - Sweet sauce
तीखी चटनी - Chilli sauce
जीरा पाउडर - Cumin powder - Roasted
काला नमक - Black salt
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli
बूंदी - Boondi

snippet.title: ഡോളറിനു പകരം ചൈനീസ് യുവാൻ? De Dollarization | End of US Dollar | Yuan Vs Dollar
snippet.description:
De Dollarization | End of US Dollar | Yuan Vs Dollar

Many countries have joined the idea of De Dollarization, the idea to remove the US dollar as the major world reserve currency. Russia and China are leading the e de-dollarization movement by replacing us dollar with the Chinese yuan. This video explains how the US dollar became a world reserve currency, the advantages of becoming the world reserve currency and how the US misused its reserve currency status to manipulate the US economy and sanction countries across the world. The video also explains the progress of the de-dollarization movement over the years including the petroyuan proposed by Saudi Arabia and China, will it lead to the end of us dollar dominance, will the Chinese Yuan replace the US dollar? and the alternative currencies including the BRICS currency.

#dedollarization #chineseyuan #usdollar

snippet.title: Viral | Narmada नदी के बीचों बीच पैदल चलती दिखी महिला, दर्शन करने उमड़ी हजारों लोगों की भीड़ | MP
snippet.description:
Viral | जबलपुर. सोशल मीडिया में गुमशुदा महिला बनी मां नर्मदा बेटी,
नर्मदा किनारे रेत पर दौड़ती ज्योतिबाई रघुवंशी का वीडियो वायरल,
बीते एक सप्ताह से शहपुरा से जबलपुर के बीच नर्मदा किनारे घूम रही हैं ज्योति बाई,
आस्था या अंधविश्वास,
ज्योतिबाई के दर्शन करने उमड़ रही हजारों लोगों की भीड़,
नर्मदापुरम पिपरिया में दर्ज है ज्योतिबाई की गुमशुदगी,
नर्मदा की बेटी मानकर ज्योतिबाई के पीछे घूम रहे हजारों लोग.

#viral #narmada #miracle #omg #narmadaparikrama #jabalpur #mpnews

snippet.description:

Farq Episode 48 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 11th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir

snippet.title: బెంగుళూరు స్పెషల్ అద్భుతమైన కారా బాత్ నీరు చట్నీ | Hotel Style Kara Bath with Neer Chutney Recipe
snippet.description:
బెంగళూర్ స్పెషల్ అద్భుతమైన కారా బాత్ నీరు చట్నీ | Hotel Style Kara bath with Neer Chutney in telugu | Bangalore Special Breakfast Kara Bath Neer Chutney

Hello Foodies!
In this video, we'll show you how to make a delicious and spicy Bangalore special Kara Bath recipe, along with a Neer Chutney that perfectly complements the dish. Kara Bath is a popular breakfast dish in Bangalore, made with semolina, vegetables, and a blend of aromatic spices. We'll show you how to make this flavorful dish step-by-step and also share some tips and tricks to make it even more delicious. And to balance out the spiciness of the Kara Bath, we'll also be making a simple and spicy Neer Chutney, made with coconut, green chilies, and coriander. This chutney is the perfect accompaniment to the Kara Bath and will leave you feeling satisfied. So, follow the steps shown in this video to learn how to make this classic Bangalore breakfast dish with a twist!

snippet.title: Farq Episode 49 Teaser - 11th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Episode 49 Teaser - 11th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Faysal Quraishi as Kamal Hassan
Sehar Khan as Irsa 
Adeel Chaudhry as Daniyal
Mahmood Aslam as Arif
Saba Shah as Ayzel
Juvaria Abbasi as Faiza 
Sohail Sameer as Rashid
Sabiha Hashmi as Husna Phuppo
Faiza Gillani as Yasmeen
Raeed Muhammad Alam as Jamshed
Aadi Khan as Mani
Farah Nadir as Razia

snippet.title: ആട് അമ്മായിക്ക് സമ്മാനവുമായി ഒരുപാട് പേർ. ഇനി നിങ്ങളുടെ പ്രാർത്ഥന മതി
snippet.description:
#emotional
#sad
#goat
#sadsong

snippet.title: ​ @buildingpanther  -  Dard-E-Dil | Official Music Video | Panther | Ankee | Pallavi
snippet.description:
The ‘MTV Hustle 2.0’ alum Panther brings to you his first love song – or rather, his first heartbreak song! Featuring Pallavi Deswal, the track is guaranteed to remind you of your ex, and the countless memories associated with them. Perfect to be shared with the one with whom you can’t share anything anymore, ‘Dard-E-Dil’ is composed, written and sung by Panther.

#DardEDil #Panther #Ankee

Audio Credits
Primary Artist - Panther, Ankee
Writer, Singer, Composer, Rapper - Panther
Producer - Ankee
Additional Guitars - Rapchari

Video credits
Director/ concept - Divyansh Joshi
Creative director - Parth Joshi, Shubham Sharma
Dop - Tushar Gupta, Ashish Bahuguna
Production - Abhimanyu Kochar, Rishabh Pandey, Sanjana Arya.
Styling / Makeup/ Art direction - Nikita Gupta, Yash Vardhan
Editor/ Color - Sumit Maurya
Spot - Vikas, Abhay
Light - Manthan, Lavi Nahal
Special thanks - D.D Joshi, Kamal Gupta, Neha Joshi 
Executive producer - Abhimanyu Kochar

Cast - 
Female Lead - Pallavi Deswal
Manoj Joshi, Sambhav Sharma, Simran Bhatt, Ravi Jain, Akshita Oli, Dipsari mondal, Anshita Rawat, Shruti Pokhriyal, Anushka Bora

Project Head - Manoj Joshi
Managed by Sambhav Thakur, Acapella Productions

Lyrics:
Suno mera dard e dil
Usne zakham dia fir wo hanske chal padi
Hum to unke muntazir
Shikwe lakho par 
Chehre pe shikan nahi
Verse

Usne jalaya humko
Mai usse jala kab
Hota Zara bata aisa insaaf kaha par
Daga kar
fir uski dawa kar
Baat bas itni si ki gaya ni tu bata kar
Tumne rulaya humko
Aansu na baha par
Hota Zara bata aisa insaaf kaha par
Jyaada sunaya tune
Aur fir Suna kam
Baat bas itni si ki gaya ni tu bata kar

Padha kar tu mere baare padha kar
Jana hai kya upar leke wafa tujhe bachakar
Hansi gaya fansakar, Hansi gayi bhula kar,
Koi ghayal na chute jab koi chorey galey lagakar,
nazm tere naam pe to deta hu kuch Bada padh
Ho gayi tu kharch, karunga kya itna kama kar
Jyaada sunaya tune
Aur fir Suna kam
Baat bas itni si ki gaya ni tu bata kar

Chorus

Suno mera dard e dil
Usne zakham dia fir wo hanske chal padi
Hum to unke muntazir
Shikwe lakho par 
Chehre pe shikan nahi

 Verse 

Kehna to hai kaafi tumse
Shayad ek baar to mang logi maafi mujhse
Log kehte Hum na reh gaye hai pehle jaise
Shayad tu reh gayi hai kaafi mujhme

Bhari duniya lagti khaali si hai
Na hu akela par akelepan ka sath bhi hai
Tu gayi to chala gaya sukoon bhi
Ab kisi jism me tere jism sa araam ni hai

Chehre kaafi par hai tera chehra nahi,
Kehte sab par koi tumsa kehta nahi,
Rehne ko hai kaafi ghar mere paas
Par na gharme hoti tu to ghar bhi gharsa lagta nahi

Sabkuch paakar bhi sab kho diya hai
Kiya itna sab par tu na to fir kyu kiya hai
Jhagadta na hai mujhse ab koi,
Apne me hu rehta kyuki apno ko hi kho dia hai

Chorus

Suno mera dard e dil
Usne zakham dia fir wo hanske chal padi
Hum to unke muntazir
Shikwe lakho par 
Chehre pe shikan nahi

snippet.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Part 1 ft. Benafsha Soonawalla | Music Prod By @BluishMusic & Sez On The beat
snippet.description:
Boyfriend is a song where Dino James portrays the insecurities and toxicity that an individual can go through in a relationship and the trauma that follows if they let themselves fall deep into the dark hole of insecurities. An uncomfortable truth that a lot of people face. Through this song, Dino James has a strong message, “If this is what people face, best for both parties to walk away. Toxicity and trauma is never okay”.

hi.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Part 1 ft. Benafsha Soonawalla | Music Prod By @BluishMusic & Sez On The beat
hi.description:
Boyfriend is a song where Dino James portrays the insecurities and toxicity that an individual can go through in a relationship and the trauma that follows if they let themselves fall deep into the dark hole of insecurities. An uncomfortable truth that a lot of people face. Through this song, Dino James has a strong message, “If this is what people face, best for both parties to walk away. Toxicity and trauma is never okay”.

snippet.description:
Presenting ৰঙালী (Rongali 2023) by Achurjya Borpatra exclusively on Achurjya Borpatra Official. 

AB Production Presents
আচুৰ্য বৰপাত্ৰৰ
ৰঙালী

কথা-সুৰ-সংগীত : অপূৰ্ব-শোণিত
টাই সংগ্ৰহ: কৃষ্ণা বৰগোহাঁই 
ঢোল - পংকজ বৰা, লাচিত বৰুৱা
পেঁপা-গগনা-ধুতং-তাল - পিতি বৰা
বীণ - গৌতম 
বাঁহী - কৈলাশ ৰাভা
সহঃ শিল্পী - জনম কাশ্যপ
শব্দ সংমিশ্ৰণ - দিগন্ত বৰদলৈ

Music Publisher: Eikhon Axom Hoi Bhai Media

Special Thanks to Saranga Bhuyan, Diganta Bordoloi, Sunit Gogoi, Jugantar Nath, Montu Gohain, Darpan Bortanuly, Saundarjya Bhuyan Hazarika, Mukunda Kalita, Luit Kakoty, Paplu Chetia, Nil Bordoloi, Manabendra Bora, Monuj Boraik, Jayanta Das, Janam Kashyap, Bhargav Khound, Trailukya Boruah, Arnab Hazarika, Bidyut Robin, Bolin Bora, Jyotishman Chetia, Suvrat Kakoti , Nitu Khanikar. 

[Lyrics]
বৰনৈ বাঢ়িলে চাপৰি বুৰিলে
টুপাই বুৰ মাৰিলে শিহু !
উজনি নামনিত ঢোলে গুমগুমালে ঐ
পালেহি ব'হাগৰ বিহু !!

অনতাংমা পাইলোছে মেচিচাংঞা ছৈনী ঐ
চমপাংক' পাইলোছে চেফ্ৰি !
চিনাংকা পাইলোছে মেচিচাং জানাং ঐ
চমপাংক' পাইলোছে চেফ্ৰি !!

ধনচেং ঢোলৰে বৰতি
ধনচেং ল'লো টানি টানি
আকৌ আহি পালেহি মৰমৰে বিহুটি
ধনচেং ধনৰ মলা , ফূলচেং ফুলৰ মলা
বিহু মাৰিবলৈ/২ যাওঁ !!

ধনচেং কঁকালৰ টঙালি
ধনচেং বান্ধিলো উজালি
ডালত পৰি বিনালে কলীয়াকৈ কুলিটি
ধনচেং ধনৰ মলা , ফুলচেং ফুলৰ মলা
বতৰৰ গীতকে/২ গাওঁ !!
আওতে ঐ পিতুৰিয়া
খামচেং পিলুং পিয়্যকা
পুলুং সজা মিটলং
পাই চিদে চং কং
কাচি ঐ কাচি ঐ কৰাক মা !!

আকৌ চেংকন গড়গঞা নাচনী
আকৌ চেংকন হালি-জালি নাচিব
আকৌ চেংকন ৰংঘৰৰ বাকৰি
আকৌ চেংকন জিলিকি উঠিব
আকৌ চেংকন মোৰে চেংকন 
পৃথৱী উঠিব/২ কঁপি !

আকৌ চেংকন আমি অসমীয়া
আকৌ চেংকন মূৰত পাগে মৰা
আকৌ চেংকন বিহু বুলি ক'লে
আকৌ চেংকন ভাতে-পানী এৰা
আকৌ চেংকন মোৰে চেংকন
নাচোনত উৰাই যাওঁ/২ ধূলি !!

চ'ততে চকৰী দদাই ঐ
ব'হাগত বাবৰি দদাই ঐ
জেঠতে আমনা দদাই ঐ ধান !
গৰুবিহুৰ দিনা দদাই ঐ
বস্ত্ৰ দান কৰিবা দদাই ঐ
তেহে পাবা বৈকুণ্ঠত দদাই ঐ স্হান !!

snippet.title: POORI | King Of Poori Recipe | Wheat Poori Recipe Cooking in Village | Crispy Fluffy Puri Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook a large quantity of wheat poori recipe. We use only wheat flour and cold pressed gingelly oil to make this poori recipe healthy and traditional.

Finally, we enjoy the puri recipe with our favorite mutton curry!

The taste is, Crispy and Yummy!

snippet.title: UNVEILING MY FIRST SUPERCAR !!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the thrilling journey of my first supercar reveal! It has been a long and exciting road to get to this point, and I am beyond thrilled to share it with all of you.

From the initial concept sketches to the countless hours of testing and refining, every step of this journey has been a labor of love. And now, finally, the moment has arrived to unveil this beauty to the world.

This journey has been a wild ride, but I couldn't be more proud of the final result. So come along with me and let's experience the excitement and awe of the first supercar reveal together!

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Episode 47 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 10th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Faysal Quraishi as Kamal Hassan
Sehar Khan as Irsa 
Adeel Chaudhry as Daniyal
Mahmood Aslam as Arif
Saba Shah as Ayzel
Juvaria Abbasi as Faiza 
Sohail Sameer as Rashid
Sabiha Hashmi as Husna Phuppo
Faiza Gillani as Yasmeen
Raeed Muhammad Alam as Jamshed
Aadi Khan as Mani
Farah Nadir as Razia

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
aarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Pandey निवास में घुसी ढोंगी! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 679
snippet.description:
Pandey निवास में घुसी ढोंगी! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 679

Thapki tries to convince Aryan that she is not an impostor. But later that night, she sneaks out of the house to go somewhere. Upon her return, Thapki finds Aryan waiting for her. Where did she go? Is she indeed the real Thapki?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Dastak Mayray Dil Pay | Episode 66 | Turkish Drama | Urdu Dubbing | SenCal Kapimi | 9th April 2023 |
snippet.description:
Dastak Mayray Dil Pay | Sen Cal Kapimi | You knock on my Door |


#Urdu1 #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed #sencalkapimi #sençalkapımı #DastakMayrayDilPay #sençalkapımı #sencalkapimi #youknockonmydoor #handeercel #handeerçel #kerembürsin #karembursin #melisadöngel #bigeönal #loveisintheair #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda’s university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan’s fiancée, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex’s wedding but pretending to be the fiancée of Istanbul’s most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.


Produced by: MF YAPIM

Shekhar Jaiswal Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/theshekharjaiswal

Other Channel - https://youtube.com/c/ShekharJaiswalComedy

Booking - 9719998366, 7451940400
Shekharredifmail@gmail.com


Lyrics -
-----------------------------------------

Lagan tumse lga baithe jo hoga dekha jayga
Tume apna bana baithe jo hoga dekha jayga..

Kaise kese du meri dua beasar ho gai
Jab bhi roya mere shambhunath ko khrab ho gai..
Nzar bholenath ki padi is kdar humpar
Nazarandaz walo ki bhi nzar ho gai..
Tume dil se laga baithe
Jo hoga dekha jayga
Lagan tumse lga baithe jo hoga dekha jayga

Nam mera hua baba tu krne wala hai
Jo bhi sankat tha mere sar me tune tala hai
Tera hi naam le lekr me sare kam kru
Kehte hai log banda kismat wala hai
Teri galiyo me aa baithe

snippet.title: Legacy - Amit Bhadana (Official Music Video) | Bintu Pabra | KP Kundu | The Kidd | Vaksh Vimal |
snippet.description:
This song is the fourth single by Amit Bhadana. After Parichay, Aatmvishvas and Father Saab now i bring you Legacy. Through Legacy I am trying to convey a simple message - If you choose not to be the part of the rat race, stay firm on your resolve and never compromise on your principles you can achieve anything under the sun. This song showcase Three major chunks of My life, one in my village where 5 years of my life were spent, second where i spent 20 years in Delhi and my present life where i am fullfilling all my dreams and taking care of my family .You will get a glimpse of my journey from village to city, days of extreme poverty in a new location and my struggle. With hardwork i overcame every hardship and created a better life for myself and my loved ones. I believe that this is just the beginning. I dream of a much better future and need every bit of your support to make it a reality. With quality content, creativity and vision I want to add value to my viewers lives. In the past 6 years I have learnt alot and taught alot (you know it better) and I wish to keep entertaining everyone for the rest of my life. I want to create a legacy that goes on from genaration to generation Please watch this song and don’t forget to share it with your family and friends. Legacy. Love.
